To get this repository:

linux $ git clone https://github.com/FF-Remote-Control/FF-Remote-Control.git

You'll probably have to do som rearranging: This will put it into
a folder caller FF-Remote-Control, and that folder will include three
.git* folders that should be removed.

Then you have to do:

linux $ make xpi-dir

That will create: 

-rw-rw-r--. 1 mccrory mccrory 47991 Nov 16 14:42 remote_control-1.3-fx.xpi

Elliott McCrory
11/16/2015
